                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-134-18611216 t18611216-134-punishment-48"></join>Confined Twelve Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">There was another indictment against the prisoner.</hi>
